Package main.java.questfortheabodeth.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Clickable  
    Collidable
    Any object that can be hit by another object must implement this class
    Interactable  
    Menu  
    Movable
    Any object that can be moved should implement this interface so that all objects on the screen can be moved as part of one single loop in the main class
    Powerup
    All main.java.questfortheabodeth.powerups implement this so that their special effect can be applied to the main.java.questfortheabodeth.characters
